{"tid":496496,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【世界末日咁】15萬隻蝙蝠襲昆士蘭小鎮 空降蝙蝠糞蝙蝠屍","createTime":"2017-12-11T17:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T06:55:08.000Z","uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2c9a0b6fef9bc0df7ad7e702d1e71e32f68f2613","tid":496496,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T17:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171211/large/1512982431_4866.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171211%2Flarge%2F1512982431_4866.jpg&h=edfefe08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「四周都是蝙蝠糞便，別說當中帶有多種疾病的蝙蝠屍體了，情況實在非常可怕。」澳洲昆士蘭一個小鎮近日有約15萬隻蝙蝠來襲，牠們的糞便影響衞生環境，叫聲亦令人煩擾，居民促州政府盡快處理問題。<br />\n<br />\n查特斯堡 (Charters Towers)一名居民指，近月蝙蝠來襲的數目是過往的3倍，四周都是蝙蝠糞便和蝙蝠屍體，嚴重威脅社區健康，但當地政府束手無策。<br />\n<br />\n從影片看到，蝙蝠數量非常多，整片天空都佈滿蝙蝠似的，牠們的糞便對環境造成嚴重污染，當地有兩個公園、一個游泳和一個保齡球會所要關閉，巿長施密特 (Liz Schmidt)直指蝙蝠對公眾和當地企業帶來負面影響，正計劃請求州政府介入協助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171212/57567600\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171212%2F57567600&d=Hu28vLA53FrRWELIgH56vQtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=18fcc797\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171212%2F57567600&h=5788e629\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171212/57567600</a><br />\n<br />\n隔住個mon都覺得煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0fb0c7575d7dc49d2b7bf30794c1dbaa9943485","tid":496496,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T00:36:54.000Z","msg":"澳洲個生態體系真是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8def2544ab1d724d219d9858cf0985670ee4ef5","tid":496496,"uid":3936